          "date": "2017-04-06 17:56:05.000000000",
          "tz": 180
        },
        "subject": "LU-8964 llite: Make readahead async",
        "message": "LU-8964 llite: Make readahead async\n\nRemoved current Lustre implementation of readahead and replaced it\nwith in-kernel implementation. Adopted code for in-kernel readahead\nusage. Perform readahead requests asynchronously from current I/O.\n\nIn combination with parallelization of generic I/O this patch allows\nsignificantly improve read performance for KNL.\n\nChange-Id: Ic2a348bb73c6a00f6c88a982fa39d11c45c1660d\nSigned-off-by: Dmitry Eremin <dmitry.eremin@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/pfl"
    }
  },
